1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,937
=Episode 13=

23
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,480
How is Shanshan?

24
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,359
She cried herself tired and fell asleep.

25
00:02:05,537 --> 00:02:07,297
But she's stronger than I expected.

26
00:02:08,137 --> 00:02:08,879
I've always hoped

27
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:10,879
Shanshan would see Zhou Zeyang
for who he really is

28
00:02:11,450 --> 00:02:12,850
and break up with him for good.

29
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,960
Now that it finally happened,

30
00:02:16,737 --> 00:02:18,800
I don't feel as happy
as I thought I would.

31
00:02:19,212 --> 00:02:20,879
It's my fault
for not stepping in sooner.

32
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,159
You were right.

33
00:02:27,362 --> 00:02:28,242
I was too arrogant.

34
00:02:31,112 --> 00:02:32,672
Shanshan keeps asking me

35
00:02:33,675 --> 00:02:36,138
why Zhou Zeyang turned out like this.

36
00:02:36,862 --> 00:02:38,680
I don't even know how to comfort her.

37
00:02:39,825 --> 00:02:41,626
Maybe Zhou Zeyang

38
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:45,039
didn't intend to use her
at the beginning.

39
00:02:45,825 --> 00:02:48,048
But once a person's greed is magnified,

40
00:02:50,512 --> 00:02:51,672
there's no bottom line.

41
00:02:53,437 --> 00:02:54,758
People change.

42
00:02:55,287 --> 00:02:56,000
What about you?

43
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,175
What would make you change?

44
00:02:59,387 --> 00:03:00,266
I don't know.

45
00:03:02,087 --> 00:03:03,840
I just hope I never do.

46
00:03:14,662 --> 00:03:15,622
But I know you.

47
00:03:16,387 --> 00:03:17,879
I also know our future.

48
00:03:19,712 --> 00:03:23,062
♪I run back along the dates♪

49
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,360
What do you know about me?

50
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,719
What will

51
00:03:28,650 --> 00:03:30,000
our future be like?

52
00:03:31,687 --> 00:03:32,520
Zhuang Yan.

53
00:03:32,987 --> 00:03:35,080
I don't know what the future holds,

54
00:03:35,737 --> 00:03:36,936
but instead of fearing the unknown,

55
00:03:36,975 --> 00:03:38,776
I want to face it with you.

56
00:03:42,962 --> 00:03:46,375
♪Let the hourglass flow backward♪

57
00:03:46,487 --> 00:03:50,150
♪I travel against time♪

58
00:03:50,537 --> 00:03:55,612
♪All regrets deserve to be remeasured♪

59
00:03:57,487 --> 00:04:03,775
♪We didn't know
that moment was already eternal♪

60
00:04:03,850 --> 00:04:13,862
♪The counter-clockwise hand
is ultimately nailed to eternity♪

61
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:23,839
So what's the surprise?

62
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:25,000
Why so mysterious?

63
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,959
Where is this?

64
00:04:32,737 --> 00:04:34,136
This is our company.

65
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,680
Ours?

66
00:04:36,125 --> 00:04:38,006
I promised I'd give you happiness.

67
00:04:39,037 --> 00:04:40,638
It may be small,

68
00:04:41,987 --> 00:04:44,588
but would you
be willing to be its only lady boss?

69
00:04:45,437 --> 00:04:46,036
I…

70
00:04:51,575 --> 00:04:52,695
Ms. Qin Jiamin.

71
00:04:54,462 --> 00:04:56,301
Will you accept my feelings?

72
00:04:57,550 --> 00:04:59,071
Will you give me a chance

73
00:04:59,612 --> 00:05:01,573
to take care of you
for the rest of my life?

74
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,160
Yes.

75
00:05:10,012 --> 00:05:11,052
Jiamin.

76
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,519
Nice skills.

77
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:32,560
What do I usually tell you guys?

78
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:34,659
Whoever they are,

79
00:05:34,887 --> 00:05:36,487
you still have to show respect.

80
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,759
I hear you've started your own company.

81
00:05:42,687 --> 00:05:45,247
Should I be calling you Mr. Zhou?

82
00:05:46,237 --> 00:05:49,877
I even thought of visiting you sometime.

83
00:05:55,442 --> 00:05:57,002
What happened to your face?

84
00:05:57,442 --> 00:05:59,787
Did Zhuang Yan beat you again?

85
00:06:00,262 --> 00:06:01,062
It wasn't Zhuang Yan.

86
00:06:02,202 --> 00:06:02,882
It was Qin Mo.

87
00:06:03,437 --> 00:06:04,036
Oh.

88
00:06:05,087 --> 00:06:05,726
No wonder.

89
00:06:06,401 --> 00:06:08,887
You tricked away
his precious little sister.

90
00:06:08,887 --> 00:06:10,401
That beating was well deserved.

91
00:06:10,642 --> 00:06:12,841
Qin Mo threw me out
in front of the whole company.

92
00:06:13,875 --> 00:06:15,235
I can't go back anymore.

93
00:06:16,401 --> 00:06:17,241
Mr. Zhang.

94
00:06:18,322 --> 00:06:20,161
Do you understand how I feel right now?

95
00:06:24,775 --> 00:06:25,856
I don't.

96
00:06:26,475 --> 00:06:27,754
And I don't want to.

97
00:06:28,637 --> 00:06:30,276
Jinxin's internal fighting

98
00:06:30,350 --> 00:06:31,831
shouldn't involve me as a pawn.

99
00:06:33,401 --> 00:06:35,202
Mr. Zhang, what are you saying?

100
00:06:36,841 --> 00:06:38,562
If Jinxin goes under,

101
00:06:39,401 --> 00:06:41,322
won't the industry be yours to rule?

102
00:06:43,642 --> 00:06:45,522
Is that your concern?

103
00:06:46,002 --> 00:06:47,841
You can barely save yourself now.

104
00:06:49,962 --> 00:06:51,241
That's not quite right.

105
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:54,238
Qin Jiamin is now my fiancée.

106
00:06:54,787 --> 00:06:56,107
Even if Qin Mo
refuses to acknowledge me,

107
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:58,138
would he really disown his own sister?

108
00:07:07,401 --> 00:07:08,721
What sneaky tricks

109
00:07:09,481 --> 00:07:11,002
do you have up your sleeve
to come see me?

110
00:07:12,801 --> 00:07:15,481
I want to discuss
a business deal with you.

111
00:07:16,642 --> 00:07:18,041
Qin Mo has gotten too arrogant.

112
00:07:18,562 --> 00:07:19,762
Why don't we join forces

113
00:07:20,401 --> 00:07:21,401
and finish him off?

114
00:07:22,962 --> 00:07:24,601
Hahaha.

115
00:07:28,041 --> 00:07:30,601
So how do you plan to work together?

116
00:07:31,137 --> 00:07:32,336
It's simple.

117
00:07:33,841 --> 00:07:35,401
If we want Qin Mo to take the bait,

118
00:07:35,587 --> 00:07:37,262
we need to raise the stakes.

119
00:07:37,787 --> 00:07:40,008
All you need to do
is give me some resources.

120
00:07:40,275 --> 00:07:42,116
I'll handle the rest.

121
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:44,081
Don't worry.

122
00:07:44,921 --> 00:07:46,522
I won't disappoint you.

123
00:07:51,442 --> 00:07:52,401
Care for a round?

124
00:07:54,401 --> 00:07:55,161
Sure.

125
00:07:57,790 --> 00:07:58,361
Rack up the balls.

126
00:07:59,721 --> 00:08:01,962
Next month's food trade fair in Haicheng

127
00:08:02,522 --> 00:08:04,801
is a perfect chance
to expand Jinxin's brand.

128
00:08:05,642 --> 00:08:07,601
I recommend Shanshan
as our spokesperson.

129
00:08:08,401 --> 00:08:11,041
And the spokesperson
should be deeply tied to the brand.

130
00:08:11,041 --> 00:08:12,002
I propose

131
00:08:12,002 --> 00:08:15,082
that Shanshan also serve
as the manager of Publicity Department

132
00:08:15,241 --> 00:08:17,401
and take charge of all promotional work.

133
00:08:18,375 --> 00:08:21,375
The spokesperson idea isn't bad,

134
00:08:21,912 --> 00:08:24,735
but Shanshan lacks experience.

135
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:27,260
Putting her
in charge of Publicity Department

136
00:08:27,887 --> 00:08:28,937
might be hard to justify.

137
00:08:28,987 --> 00:08:30,437
When I first joined,

138
00:08:31,062 --> 00:08:32,381
you said the same about me.

139
00:08:33,462 --> 00:08:34,503
I think Shanshan can do it.

140
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,519
Forget manager.

141
00:08:36,637 --> 00:08:38,062
She could even take your place...

142
00:08:38,212 --> 00:08:39,150
Yan.

143
00:08:39,241 --> 00:08:39,962
Qin.

144
00:08:39,962 --> 00:08:41,402
Don't listen to Yan's nonsense.

145
00:08:41,402 --> 00:08:43,360
I'm not qualified to be
the manager of Publicity Department

146
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,301
Shanshan.

147
00:08:45,225 --> 00:08:46,544
Do you like working at Jinxin?

148
00:08:48,202 --> 00:08:48,442
Yeah.

149
00:08:49,922 --> 00:08:51,442
Be brave and do it then.

150
00:08:51,802 --> 00:08:52,402
Don't overthink it.

151
00:08:52,725 --> 00:08:53,725
I've got your back.

152
00:09:02,001 --> 00:09:04,282
I hereby announce that Zhuang Shanshan

153
00:09:04,721 --> 00:09:06,641
will serve
as our company's food spokesperson

154
00:09:06,641 --> 00:09:08,841
and concurrently
as the manager of Publicity Department.

155
00:09:09,641 --> 00:09:11,001
- Great.
- Great.

156
00:09:12,601 --> 00:09:13,361
Great news.

157
00:09:13,442 --> 00:09:14,601
I object.

158
00:09:21,402 --> 00:09:22,202
Qin Jiamin.

159
00:09:23,562 --> 00:09:25,641
You're no longer a Jinxin employee.

160
00:09:25,962 --> 00:09:27,001
You have no right to interfere.

161
00:09:27,402 --> 00:09:28,202
One more thing,

162
00:09:28,675 --> 00:09:29,994
the two people behind you

163
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:31,721
aren't welcomed here.

164
00:09:32,601 --> 00:09:33,121
Li.

165
00:09:33,282 --> 00:09:33,761
Yes.

166
00:09:34,042 --> 00:09:34,601
Show them out.

167
00:09:35,121 --> 00:09:36,562
I may not be an employee,

168
00:09:36,562 --> 00:09:38,001
but I'm still a shareholder.

169
00:09:38,361 --> 00:09:40,282
I'm here today to formally notify you

170
00:09:40,282 --> 00:09:42,601
that I've decided to sell my 10% stake

171
00:09:42,601 --> 00:09:44,202
to Mr. Zhang Guolong.

172
00:09:44,537 --> 00:09:45,336
Yeah.

173
00:09:50,361 --> 00:09:51,641
According to company rules,

174
00:09:52,162 --> 00:09:53,641
family members have priority

175
00:09:53,787 --> 00:09:55,195
when shares are transferred.

176
00:09:56,162 --> 00:09:57,072
I'm your brother.

177
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:59,240
If you're selling your shares,

178
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,475
I should be first in line.

179
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:02,480
You already kicked me out
of the Qin family

180
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,020
and said you don't acknowledge
me as your sister.

181
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,399
Even without family ties,

182
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:10,879
we can still do business.

183
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:13,159
Ms. Qin wants to sell her shares,

184
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:15,200
and I happen to afford them.

185
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:17,159
Buyer and seller both agreed.

186
00:10:17,159 --> 00:10:19,279
Why insist on getting in the way?

187
00:10:19,519 --> 00:10:20,240
Zhang Guolong.

188
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,080
Do you think this is your billiard hall?

189
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,960
Our company has its own rules.

190
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,399
The shares are under my name.

191
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,000
I'm just here to inform you.

192
00:10:32,399 --> 00:10:33,200
Mr. Qin.

193
00:10:34,879 --> 00:10:36,759
We're partners from now...

194
00:10:41,559 --> 00:10:42,840
We're partners from now on.

195
00:10:54,087 --> 00:10:56,286
Why give Qin Jiamin 10% shares?

196
00:10:56,575 --> 00:10:57,896
She has only been here a few years.

197
00:10:57,896 --> 00:10:58,987
Even Shanshan has less.

198
00:11:00,175 --> 00:11:01,410
Why compare with Shanshan?

199
00:11:01,662 --> 00:11:03,112
Why not compare with Shanshan?

200
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,159
Zhuang Yan.

201
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,960
You think I'm being biased

202
00:11:08,279 --> 00:11:09,879
that I give the benefits
to my sister first?

203
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:10,840
Is it now?

204
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:12,519
Jinxin belonged to the Zhuang family.

205
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:14,639
Can you honestly say
you have absolutely no selfish motives?

206
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,080
If I were selfish,

207
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,960
I wouldn't have kicked my sister out.

208
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:20,000
If I wanted to harm Jinxin,

209
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:21,799
why not

210
00:11:21,799 --> 00:11:23,759
sell the shares to Zhang Guolong?

211
00:11:30,159 --> 00:11:31,120
No matter what,

212
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,919
I will help Shanshan get back
everything that's hers.

213
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,279
Why are you here?

214
00:11:46,279 --> 00:11:47,159
Speak quickly.

215
00:11:47,159 --> 00:11:48,240
We're not that close.

216
00:11:48,975 --> 00:11:50,735
The day I broke up with Zhou Zeyang,

217
00:11:51,275 --> 00:11:52,714
I thought about ending my life.

218
00:11:53,159 --> 00:11:54,240
Don't play the victim with me.

219
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,440
I won't fall for it.

220
00:11:55,562 --> 00:11:56,562
But I didn't.

221
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,680
Because I knew

222
00:11:58,875 --> 00:12:00,914
if I ended my life over you interfering

223
00:12:00,914 --> 00:12:01,955
with Zhou Zeyang,

224
00:12:02,037 --> 00:12:03,799
Qin would blame himself forever.

225
00:12:04,037 --> 00:12:05,399
He wouldn't forgive you either.

226
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,960
I don't want you two
to turn against each other.

227
00:12:08,312 --> 00:12:10,871
I know how much Qin values you.

228
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,000
We've already turned against each other,

229
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,000
and it's because of you.

230
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:16,360
Zhuang Shanshan.

231
00:12:16,639 --> 00:12:18,159
I know why you came today.

232
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:19,360
Don't waste your effort.

233
00:12:19,425 --> 00:12:21,879
I will sell that 10% share.

234
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:25,080
You know Zhang Guolong's relationship
with Qin.

235
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,559
You're also aware

236
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:29,000
what it would mean for Jinxin

237
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:30,360
if Zhang Guolong gets that 10% share.

238
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:33,840
Jiamin, will you risk Jinxin's future

239
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,262
for Zhou Zeyang?

240
00:12:35,525 --> 00:12:37,565
Why should I care about Jinxin's future?

241
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,000
Didn't your good cousin

242
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,279
always claim

243
00:12:40,279 --> 00:12:42,425
that Jinxin is your family's property?

244
00:12:42,537 --> 00:12:43,440
You can't even

245
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,360
protect your own property.

246
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:44,960
Who can you blame?

247
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,879
Yan didn't mean that.

248
00:12:46,879 --> 00:12:49,262
I've never treated
Jinxin as my property.

249
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:51,879
Zhuang Shanshan, spare it.

250
00:12:52,039 --> 00:12:53,840
I've long been tired

251
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:54,840
of your innocent pretense.

252
00:12:55,175 --> 00:12:57,039
If you have time
to play the victim here,

253
00:12:57,150 --> 00:12:59,720
you'd better cling
to my brother and Zhuang Yan.

254
00:13:01,450 --> 00:13:01,919
Jiamin.

255
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,240
What exactly do you want

256
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,960
to not sell the shares to Zhang Guolong?

257
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:05,679
Just say it,

258
00:13:05,679 --> 00:13:06,562
and I'll do it.

259
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:11,360
You said it yourself.

260
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,175
Don't regret it.

261
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:13,919
I won't regret it.

262
00:13:13,987 --> 00:13:15,725
At the food fair a month from now.

263
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,440
I want a fair contest with you.

264
00:13:22,475 --> 00:13:23,555
I will compete with you.

265
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,240
Shanshan.

266
00:13:38,279 --> 00:13:40,200
Yan, what brings you here?

267
00:13:41,159 --> 00:13:42,080
Why haven't you eaten

268
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,080
and come here alone?

269
00:13:44,075 --> 00:13:45,233
I have a bet with Jiamin.

270
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:47,750
Whoever can sign more deals
at the food fair

271
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:48,390
will win.

272
00:13:48,712 --> 00:13:49,712
If I win,

273
00:13:49,712 --> 00:13:51,612
Jiamin won't sell the shares
to Zhang Guolong.

274
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,399
Didn't you suggest
I be the spokesperson?

275
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,279
I want to form a dance troupe.

276
00:13:56,279 --> 00:13:57,559
It might give me an edge.

277
00:14:00,799 --> 00:14:02,639
If I lose,

278
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:05,960
we both have to leave
Haicheng and Jinxin.

279
00:14:06,639 --> 00:14:07,200
Oh.

280
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:08,399
Fine.

281
00:14:08,399 --> 00:14:09,679
You didn't consult me either.

282
00:14:09,879 --> 00:14:12,080
Sorry, Yan.

283
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:14,000
This was Jiamin's condition.

284
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,159
I can only accept it fully.

285
00:14:15,562 --> 00:14:16,442
But don't worry.

286
00:14:16,512 --> 00:14:17,953
I will give it my all.

287
00:14:18,050 --> 00:14:19,050
I will fight to win.

288
00:14:20,879 --> 00:14:22,559
It's okay even if you lose.

289
00:14:22,559 --> 00:14:23,639
I'm here too.

290
00:14:24,399 --> 00:14:25,200
I'll handle the aftermath.

291
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,679
No, Yan.

292
00:14:25,679 --> 00:14:26,399
Don't worry.

293
00:14:26,650 --> 00:14:28,425
This time, I'll rely on my own skills

294
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:30,039
to compete fairly with Jiamin.

295
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,440
Even if I lose,

296
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,600
I will lose honorably.

297
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:35,440
Just remember to want to win,

298
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,360
trust yourself,

299
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,799
and give it your all.

300
00:14:39,900 --> 00:14:41,790
You've been capable
of standing on your own for a long time.

301
00:14:50,050 --> 00:14:51,009
Why do you want to see me?

302
00:14:51,175 --> 00:14:52,256
I'm busy.

303
00:15:03,450 --> 00:15:05,220
I still want to explain

304
00:15:05,879 --> 00:15:07,360
about Jiamin's 10% shares.

305
00:15:07,962 --> 00:15:08,962
I didn't give them to her.

306
00:15:09,212 --> 00:15:10,370
Mr. Zhuang did.

307
00:15:11,637 --> 00:15:12,478
Mr. Zhuang?

308
00:15:15,679 --> 00:15:16,720
Shanshan's dad?

309
00:15:18,725 --> 00:15:19,125
Yes.

310
00:15:20,575 --> 00:15:23,376
Back then, Jinxin
faced a crisis from poor decisions.

311
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:26,281
Jiamin single-handedly
opened the Yuecheng market,

312
00:15:26,281 --> 00:15:27,161
raised funds,

313
00:15:27,587 --> 00:15:29,148
and helped Jinxin go through it.

314
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,279
Since then,

315
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,000
Mr. Zhuang wanted to retire.

316
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:35,039
That's why he entrusted Jinxin to me

317
00:15:35,787 --> 00:15:37,787
and gave Jiamin 10% shares.

318
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:40,580
He hoped we siblings
would protect Jinxin

319
00:15:40,580 --> 00:15:41,580
together.

320
00:15:43,039 --> 00:15:44,159
So

321
00:15:44,562 --> 00:15:47,243
you and Qin Jiamin
are the heirs he chose.

322
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,039
What does Shanshan

323
00:15:50,412 --> 00:15:51,491
mean to him?

324
00:15:52,159 --> 00:15:53,759
He just thinks her talent

325
00:15:53,759 --> 00:15:55,200
is not for running a business.

326
00:15:55,537 --> 00:15:58,212
He didn't want her
trapped in the business world's schemes.

327
00:15:59,250 --> 00:16:00,769
He protected Shanshan

328
00:16:00,837 --> 00:16:02,717
by placing her in the troupe.

329
00:16:02,879 --> 00:16:04,279
So in his opinion,

330
00:16:04,387 --> 00:16:07,307
Shanshan is born to be
a flower in a greenhouse,

331
00:16:07,425 --> 00:16:09,609
always living under protection.

332
00:16:09,762 --> 00:16:11,075
But has he thought

333
00:16:11,312 --> 00:16:12,679
how miserable a defenseless Shanshan

334
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:14,080
might be?

335
00:16:14,575 --> 00:16:17,440
He just didn't want to force Shanshan
into things she's not good at.

336
00:16:19,679 --> 00:16:21,559
But he also stifled her potential.

337
00:16:21,975 --> 00:16:24,176
This is a more arrogant denial
than looking down on her.

338
00:16:26,150 --> 00:16:26,990
Qin Mo.

339
00:16:27,975 --> 00:16:29,725
The person I knew, who's like you,

340
00:16:29,725 --> 00:16:30,925
did one thing well.

341
00:16:32,162 --> 00:16:34,002
He respected others' fate.

342
00:16:35,662 --> 00:16:37,604
He never cared if I flew high

343
00:16:37,604 --> 00:16:38,405
or tired.

344
00:16:39,087 --> 00:16:41,087
But he would never break my wings.

345
00:16:42,962 --> 00:16:45,202
Shanshan is giving her all
for this contest.

346
00:16:45,425 --> 00:16:47,025
I bet she will amaze everyone.

347
00:16:58,879 --> 00:16:59,960
Hey, Ms. Zhuang.

348
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:03,080
Here is a letter for Miss Shanshan
from abroad.

349
00:17:12,037 --> 00:17:13,787
(The Juilliard School Registration Form)

350
00:17:13,787 --> 00:17:15,506
(Music school enrollment form?)

351
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,559
Always late or early,

352
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:20,839
you only show up

353
00:17:20,839 --> 00:17:22,880
when Shanshan
is finally interested in Jinxin.

354
00:17:48,112 --> 00:17:51,750
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

355
00:17:51,875 --> 00:17:55,187
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

356
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:58,937
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

357
00:17:59,237 --> 00:18:02,525
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

358
00:18:02,750 --> 00:18:06,375
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

359
00:18:06,537 --> 00:18:09,875
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

360
00:18:09,950 --> 00:18:13,662
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

361
00:18:13,712 --> 00:18:17,575
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

362
00:18:17,637 --> 00:18:23,687
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

363
00:18:24,862 --> 00:18:31,600
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

364
00:18:31,887 --> 00:18:36,162
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

365
00:18:36,162 --> 00:18:39,462
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

366
00:18:39,537 --> 00:18:43,837
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

367
00:18:43,900 --> 00:18:47,550
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

368
00:18:47,550 --> 00:18:51,112
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

369
00:18:51,162 --> 00:18:54,425
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

370
00:18:54,425 --> 00:18:58,175
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

371
00:18:58,175 --> 00:19:04,887
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
